OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FStare at smokers to stop   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fthem, HK health chief says 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, People in Hong Kong should discourage  
OL,6, smoking by staring at anyone who lights
OL,7, up in areas where it is banned, the    
OL,8, city's health secretary has suggested. 
OL,10,FAnswering questions about how to create
OL,11,Fa tobacco-free city, Lo Chung-mau also 
OL,12,Fsaid police could not be expected to   
OL,13,Fcatch smokers.                         
OL,15,FHong Kong is currently debating        
OL,16,Ftoughening its anti-tobacco measures.  
OL,18,FCurrent rules ban smoking inside       
OL,19,Frestaurants, workplaces, indoor public 
OL,20,Fspaces and some outdoor public areas.  
